data.description: Charming beach cottage just footsteps to the sand! This adorable 2BR/2BA coastal retreat is perfectly situated between the ocean and intracoastal, where gorgeous sunrises and sunsets are just outside your door. Upon entry, you’ll be greeted by a comfortable open floor plan that quickly makes you feel right at home. There are vaulted ceilings in the main living space and nearly every room has french doors, so there is an abundance of beautiful, natural light. The kitchen opens to the living and dining areas, making entertaining a breeze. There's even a cozy screened porch perfect for relaxing after a day at the beach. Other features include fresh interior paint, new ceiling fans and light fixtures, new carpet in the bedrooms and neutral tile flooring throughout. You can also enjoy peace of mind as several practical updates have been addressed, including a new roof and AC in 2021 and a new hot water heater in 2022. Outside you’ll find a low maintenance exterior, ample backyard space and a brick paver front yard that's brimming with seaside character. There's plenty of room for all of your beach gear in the 2 car garage. And the home has never experienced water intrusion. There’s no HOA and there’s a brand new beach walkover right across the street, giving the property outstanding short term rental potential. Some furnishings are available for purchase. Start living the beach life you’ve been dreaming of!
